    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2007-07-19</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2007-09-27T19:39:01Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Food Marketing in Schools Assessment Act - Directs the Secretary of Education to study and report to the Congress on the marketing of food and beverages in middle and high schools. </p> <p>Requires such study to assess the nutritional quality of such foods, the media through which they are marketed to children in such schools, and mechanisms that regulate such marketing.</p> <p>Directs the Secretary to collaborate in the conduct of such study with the Division of Adolescent and School Health of the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
